smission spectra versus chemical potential\nshows that one can, in principle, adjust the width of the photonic band gap by\ntuning the chemical potential via a gate voltage.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Aug 2017 01:20:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-11"}
