 optimal disturbances is shown to\nresult in less energy gain than found for either the optimal perturbations or\nthe WKB approximation due to non-normal effects that cause absorption of\ndisturbance energy into the leading face of the wave.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Aug 2017 15:22:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-14"}
